<h2>International PGP Programs</h2>

The PGP currently enrolls U.S. citizens and permanent residents only. However, we are actively expanding the project with collaborators in countries outside the United States. By registering your interest, along with your country of citizenship, you can help us prioritize our international expansion efforts. We will notify you when more information is available about our international programs.

<%= error_messages_for :international_participant, :header_message => 'Error: data could not be saved.', :message => nil %>

<p><strong>If you are a U.S citizen or permanent resident, please <%= link_to 'click here here to enroll', :signup -%>.</strong></p>

<%= form_for @international_participant do |f| %>

  <p>
    <%= f.label :email, 'E-mail address' %><br />
    <%= f.text_field :email %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= f.label :country, 'Country' %><br />
    <%= f.country_select :country %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= f.submit "Subscribe" %>
  </p>
<% end %>
